138
00:11:16,442 --> 00:11:18,778
Kaya may gusto si Fifth Prince diyan.

139
00:11:18,978 --> 00:11:22,014
Kung gayon, hindi kita matutulungan diyan.

140
00:11:52,278 --> 00:11:53,512
Magandang Yanzhi,

141
00:11:54,046 --> 00:11:55,915
hayaan mo akong magpahinga nang ilang araw.

142
00:11:57,450 --> 00:11:58,560
Nakatadhana akong maging isang prinsipeng walang ginagawa

143
00:11:58,584 --> 00:12:00,019
