ilang mga bagay.

188
00:15:53,852 --> 00:15:55,363
Bumuo ng alyansa sina Su He at Yin Zhou,

189
00:15:55,387 --> 00:15:56,867
at pinagbabantaan ka ni Su He,

190
00:15:57,089 --> 00:15:57,923
