191
00:15:57,924 --> 00:15:58,957
Tama ba 'yan?

192
00:15:59,625 --> 00:16:00,769
Paano kayong dalawa nasangkot?

193
00:16:00,793 --> 00:16:01,760
Sabihin mo sa akin ang totoo.

194
00:16:01,794 --> 00:16:02,661
Sabihin mo agad,

195
00:16:02,662 --> 00:16:04,295
para makahanap ako ng paraan para
matulungan kang makaalis dito.

196
00:16:04,296 --> 00:16:05,497
Nakalimutan na ba ng Kamahalan

197
00:16:06,231 --> 00:16:07,742
na ako ang prinsipe ng tribong Talhan,

198
00:16:07,766 --> 00:16:09,406
