615
00:37:37,321 --> 00:37:39,623
Ngunit ngayon sa pag-aaral ng imperyo,

616
00:37:39,624 --> 00:37:42,627
Pinagbantaan niya ako gamit ang
pribadong selyo ng Yunshang Pavilion.

617
00:37:44,128 --> 00:37:45,795
That day at Yunshang Pavilion,

618
00:37:45,796 --> 00:37:47,664
